{"type":null,"faqId":44487,"title":"如何升级手机？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-with-next.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;keep-together.within-page:always;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.25in;margin-left:1.0381944in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p6{text-indent:0.072916664in;margin-left:0.70902777in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p7{text-indent:0.14583333in;margin-left:0.70902777in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p8{text-indent:0.072916664in;margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.19791667in;}\n.s2{color:blue;}\n.s3{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=159317\" style=\"width:0.93680555in;height:0.43680555in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>为防止手机内存中的用户数据（如：联系人、信息、通话记录等）在升级时被删除，建议升级前备份手机数据。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在线升级：在线升级前，请连接移动网络或 WLAN。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>进入“设置”界面，点击“手机升级 &gt; 系统软件更新 &gt; 在线升级”，根据屏幕提示完成升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>本地升级：进入</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s2\">华为官网软件下载地址</span></a><span>(</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm\"><span class=\"s2\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm</span></a><span>)下载软件升级包，参考升级包中的升级指导完成升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>若手机支持 OTG 功能，也可以通过外接存储设备升级：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p6\">\n<span> 1. 使用 USB OTG 数据线连接手机和 U 盘（请使用华为认可的 USB OTG 数据线，如需购买，请访问华为商城或联系供应商）。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p7\">\n<span>2. 进入</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s2\">华为官网软件下载地址</span></a><span>(</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm\"><span class=\"s2\">http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm</span></a><span>)下载软件升级包，并将 </span><span class=\"s3\">dload</span><span> 文件夹放入 U 盘根目录下。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p8\">\n<span>3. 进入“设置”界面，点击“手机升级 &gt; 系统软件更新 &gt; U 盘升级”，根据屏幕提示完成升级。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":141,"faqType":"备份恢复与升级","useful":1,"unUseful":2,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9987","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Backup-Restore-Update","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442400812000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":161,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"升级,手机","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}